urls.title: After delighting kids on Make-A-Wish flights for years, Alaska pilots never imagined one would be for them
urls.description: Captain Ryan McNelis and First Officer Bethany McNelis have each piloted Make-A-Wish flights over their careers with Alaska Airlines. They never in a million years imagined they’d be on a Make-A-Wi…

data.text: It was an honor to care for 5-year-old Maeve as she traveled to Orlando with @MakeAWishAKWA after a brave battle with cancer.
